<p>Groups are used to organize contacts. To create a group, use the Group - New 
Group menu item or the New Group menu item. Groups can be shared with other 
users via groups subscriptions by selecting that option in the New Group form.</p>

<p>To add a contact to a group, simply click on and drag the card into the group 
listed on the left side. </p>

<p>To remove a contact from a group, click on the group, then on the card, and 
then click the Card - Remove Card from Group menu item.</p>
